'''2010年木星撞击事件'''是2010年時在[[木星|木星]]发生的[[流星体|大陨石]][[撞击事件|撞击事件]]，撞击物可能是直径约8–13米的[[小行星|小行星]]、[[彗星|彗星]]、[[半人马小行星|半人马小行星]]、[[熄火彗星|熄火彗星]]或被木星引力临时捕获的[[木星卫星|卫星]]。

== 观测 ==
此次撞击事件的过程是由[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[天文爱好者|天文爱好者]]安东尼·韦斯利（Anthony Wesley）在2010年6月3日发现并第一个报告。[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]天文爱好者克里斯托弗·郭（Christopher Go）也拍摄影片而同时记录这次事件。<ref name=sayanagi>{{cite web |title=Jupiter hit by another impactor Thursday |first=Kunio M. |last=Sayanagi |url=http://arstechnica.com/science/news/2010/06/breaking-news-jupiter-hit-by-yet-another-impactor.ars |date=3 June 2010 |accessdate=4 June 2010 |publisher=Ars Technica |archive-date=2010-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605113554/http://arstechnica.com/science/news/2010/06/breaking-news-jupiter-hit-by-yet-another-impactor.ars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=bakich>{{cite web| url=http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=9918| title=Another impact on Jupiter| date=4 June 2010| first=Michael| last=Bakich| work=[[天文學_(雜誌)|天文學 (雜誌)]] online| accessdate=4 June 2010| archive-date=2010-06-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609093512/http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=9918| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.christone.net/astro/jupiter/index.htm|title=Jupiter 2016-17 by Chris Go<!-- 机器人生成的标题 -->|accessdate=2012-02-24|archive-date=2017-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401081433/http://www.christone.net/astro/jupiter/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这次撞击事件的观测持续约2秒<ref name=sayanagi/><ref name=dailytelegraph>{{cite news |title=Australian amateur astronomer Anthony Wesley films Jupiter impact |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/news/nsw-act/amateur-australian-astronomer-anthony-wesley-films-jupiter-impact/story-e6freuzi-1225875569064 |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=5 June 2010 |accessdate=4 June 2010 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822054500/https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/news/nsw/amateur-australian-astronomer-anthony-wesley-films-jupiter-impact/news-story/8404a81130073a4249fd969ac7e7a6a9?nk=05da4a3fc5f853a8c56cb33f0579d0cd-1566452700 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位于[[木星大氣層|木星大氣層]]的南赤道带区，距离中央子午线约50度。<ref name=Rogers>{{cite web |title=New impact on Jupiter before & after |first=John H. |last=Rogers |url=http://alpo-j.asahikawa-med.ac.jp/kk10/j100604r.htm |accessdate=4 June 2010 |publisher=British Astronomical Association |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609231034/http://alpo-j.asahikawa-med.ac.jp/kk10/j100604r.htm |archive-date=2010-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。撞击物的直径约为8–13米，质量为500-2000[[公顿|千吨]]。<ref name="Gemini">{{cite web |date=2010-09-09 |title=WITHOUT A TRACE – A FLASH IN JUPITER'S SKY |publisher=[[雙子星天文台|雙子星天文台]] |url=http://www.gemini.edu/node/11527 |accessdate=2010-09-09 |archive-date=2010-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918072147/http://www.gemini.edu/node/11527 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 木星每年都会被这种级别的天体撞击数次。<ref name="Gemini"/> 2010年8月20日，又发现了另一次新的木星撞击事件<ref name="Aug2010">{{cite web |title=Optical flash on Jupiter |url=http://chiron.mtk.nao.ac.jp/watanabe/optical-flash-on-jupiter |accessdate=2010-08-23 |archive-date=2010-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825010137/http://chiron.mtk.nao.ac.jp/watanabe/optical-flash-on-jupiter |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在8月23日，又有两个天文爱好者观测到撞击事件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skyandtelescope.com/community/skyblog/observingblog/101264994.html|title=Another Flash on Jupiter!|last=Beatty|first=Kelly|date=22 August 2010|work=[[Sky_&_Telescope|Sky & Telescope]]|publisher=Sky Publishing|quote=Masayuki Tachikawa was observing ... 18:22 Universal Time on the 20th ... Kazuo Aoki posted an image ... Ishimaru of Toyama prefecture observed the event|accessdate=23 August 2010|archive-date=2010-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100827180208/http://www.skyandtelescope.com/community/skyblog/observingblog/101264994.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

